00:13:18.440 --> 00:13:20.509
Rapture.

00:13:23.120 --> 00:13:26.430
We're not appointed unto wrath. God is

00:13:26.430 --> 00:13:26.440
not a wife-beater;

00:13:26.440 --> 00:13:29.470
he is not going

00:13:29.480 --> 00:13:32.509
to beat his bride. He loves us.

00:13:43.760 --> 00:13:45.790
For me and my

00:13:45.800 --> 00:13:47.670
house, we're going in the Rapture.

00:13:51.360 --> 00:13:54.870
I want to pray

00:13:57.959 --> 00:14:00.470
for the safety of America. We have open

00:14:00.480 --> 00:14:03.069
borders from a rogue president

00:14:03.069 --> 00:14:03.079
who

00:14:03.079 --> 00:14:04.470
doesn't know what he's doing,

00:14:04.480 --> 00:14:06.430
and

00:14:06.440 --> 00:14:08.829
people are pouring over. It's

00:14:08.839 --> 00:14:10.310
not just people seeking refuge; there

00:14:10.310 --> 00:14:10.320
are

00:14:10.320 --> 00:14:12.230
terrorists.

00:14:21.320 --> 00:14:23.629
This isn't Hollywood;

00:14:23.629 --> 00:14:23.639
it's

00:14:23.639 --> 00:14:27.030
real life.

00:20:43.440 --> 00:20:46.230
I see mountains

00:20:46.240 --> 00:20:49.510
right now and

00:20:49.520 --> 00:20:52.310
hidden

00:20:52.320 --> 00:20:57.110
things in

00:20:57.110 --> 00:20:57.120
Iran—hills

00:20:57.120 --> 00:20:59.029
and

00:20:59.039 --> 00:21:02.470
caves

00:21:02.480 --> 00:21:21.590
with hidden

00:21:21.600 --> 00:21:24.750
things. The

00:21:24.760 --> 00:21:27.510
Lord said the Israeli

00:21:27.520 --> 00:21:57.029
intelligence knows about these

00:21:57.039 --> 00:22:11.630
things.

00:22:42.960 --> 00:22:47.430
I see

00:22:47.440 --> 00:22:50.430
canisters; they're like silver

00:22:50.440 --> 00:22:55.750
canisters full of

00:22:55.760 --> 00:22:58.510
liquids, some of them gas. They are

00:22:58.520 --> 00:23:01.510
like

00:23:18.200 --> 00:23:26.870
huge kegs

00:23:26.880 --> 00:23:53.190
in

00:23:53.200 --> 00:23:54.990
an

00:23:55.000 --> 00:23:56.870
underground tunnel

00:23:56.880 --> 00:24:08.430
system.

00:24:12.440 --> 00:24:16.909
I see a yellow mustard

00:24:16.919 --> 00:24:26.789
gas; it is a gas in these, these

00:24:35.149 --> 00:24:35.159
Agent

00:24:39.720 --> 00:24:56.750
Orange.

00:25:09.440 --> 00:25:11.310
It's

00:25:11.320 --> 00:25:26.669
neurological.

00:25:50.840 --> 00:25:53.990
I see

00:25:59.760 --> 00:26:02.789
a

00:26:09.600 --> 00:26:12.750
long

00:26:12.760 --> 00:26:21.070
truck, and they are trying to transport these things.

00:26:25.559 --> 00:26:28.389
I see them trying to

00:26:28.389 --> 00:26:28.399
sneak

00:26:28.399 --> 00:26:29.590
the back

00:26:29.600 --> 00:26:32.830
way through the hills.

00:26:35.240 --> 00:26:38.190
It's coming

00:26:38.200 --> 00:26:41.350
through

00:26:56.600 --> 00:27:02.050
Damascus.

00:27:33.200 --> 00:27:38.230
I call every hidden thing to be

00:27:38.240 --> 00:27:43.470
exposed

00:27:43.480 --> 00:27:47.470
in the name of

00:27:47.480 --> 00:27:50.669
Jesus.

00:27:59.240 --> 00:28:01.430
I thank you, Lord, that you're

00:28:01.440 --> 00:28:03.190
guiding the

00:28:03.190 --> 00:28:03.200
intelligence and

00:28:03.200 --> 00:28:05.630
speaking to them

00:28:05.640 --> 00:28:26.430
through signs.

00:28:43.679 --> 00:28:48.310
I just saw Iraq flash before

00:28:50.320 --> 00:28:53.029
me—the

00:28:56.240 --> 00:28:58.509
northern part.

00:29:09.000 --> 00:29:26.310
I see

00:29:53.159 --> 00:29:55.389
Jordan,

00:30:21.760 --> 00:30:26.230
going clear into

00:30:26.240 --> 00:30:32.990
Syria.

00:30:33.000 --> 00:30:35.950
I see them chanting 'Death to

00:30:45.960 --> 00:30:49.549
America.'It's

00:31:05.639 --> 00:31:21.710
a rising up of so much

00:31:21.720 --> 00:31:23.710
hatred.

00:31:23.720 --> 00:31:26.190
Lord,

00:31:29.440 --> 00:31:31.789
about

00:31:37.509 --> 00:31:37.519
that

00:31:50.549 --> 00:31:50.559
gas—it

00:32:00.440 --> 00:32:02.789
makes the victim throw up and

00:32:02.789 --> 00:32:02.799
causes convulsions.

00:32:02.799 --> 00:32:06.909
It

00:32:16.830 --> 00:32:16.840
causes

00:32:25.320 --> 00:32:30.110
huge burns and

00:32:30.110 --> 00:32:30.120
welts

00:32:30.120 --> 00:32:33.389
upon the skin. I see

00:32:33.389 --> 00:32:33.399
welts

00:32:33.399 --> 00:32:36.310
like your skin is

00:32:36.320 --> 00:32:40.950
melting.

00:33:05.200 --> 00:33:07.470
We pray for

00:33:07.480 --> 00:33:21.830
protection against this evil

00:33:21.840 --> 00:33:25.230
activity.

00:33:29.039 --> 00:33:51.590
I thank you,

00:35:10.960 --> 00:35:14.870
Lord,

00:35:19.720 --> 00:35:22.109
that no weapon

00:35:22.119 --> 00:35:25.790
formed against us would

00:35:25.800 --> 00:35:33.510
prosper.

00:36:08.200 --> 00:36:09.510
I'm going to end this

00:36:09.520 --> 00:36:11.990
video here and pray over this

00:36:12.000 --> 00:36:14.430
some

00:36:14.440 --> 00:36:16.790
more.

00:36:34.839 --> 00:36:37.710
Put a

00:36:37.720 --> 00:36:39.069
smile on your face;

00:36:39.079 --> 00:36:41.510
Jesus loves you so much.

00:36:41.520 --> 00:36:44.150
God bless you

00:36:44.160 --> 00:36:47.880
guys; have a nice day.

